review_text: I used the ATM and needed smaller bills so I entered the line to exchange my bills with the teller. The manager of the branch was finishing up a conversation with the teller. Said Manager then asked me if I was a bank member. The relavancy of this question defies logic. I responded in the affirmative and then proceeded and interracted with the teller. However, I would be remiss if I did not convey my disappointment in the lack of professionalism exhibited by the manager. This reflects poorly on Fifth Third Bank.

I really enjoy stopping by this location to cash checks. Yes, I know I could deposit them via my phone - but I enjoy the friendly human interaction and Natasa is one of the most pleasant tellers I’ve ever met. She’s been very helpful in updating details in my account as well.
Beautiful new branch! Very modern, and great service!
